WEBVTT

00:03:28.945 --> 00:03:30.118
What should we do?

00:03:30.142 --> 00:03:31.308
Audience: Save it!

00:03:31.332 --> 00:03:33.089
David Cage: Save it? Save the fish?

00:03:37.808 --> 00:03:38.958
(Video) (Fish plops)

00:03:38.982 --> 00:03:40.132
DC: There we go.

00:03:41.788 --> 00:03:44.002
OK, we have an android who likes animals.

00:03:44.026 --> 00:03:45.240
OK, let's move on.

00:03:45.264 --> 00:03:47.413
Remember, we have a hostage situation.

00:03:47.804 --> 00:03:51.281
(Video) Woman: Please, please,
you've got to save my little girl!

00:03:51.305 --> 00:03:54.948
Wait -- you're sending an android?

00:03:54.972 --> 00:03:57.004
Officer: All right, ma'am, you need to go.

00:03:57.028 --> 00:03:59.347
W: You can't do that!

00:03:59.371 --> 00:04:01.810
Why aren't you sending a real person?